激活过程分为两部分——<strong>KMS激活和WMC激活</strong><br />
<h3>
<strong><u>1、KMS激活：</u></strong></h3>
1、下载RayMai制作的KMS激活器<br />
2、解压缩取出里面的bat文件<br />
3、以管理员的身份<strong>运行KMS激活器（Run As Administrator）</strong><br />
<a href="http://lh6.ggpht.com/-zzimnkDe4f4/UJS2NvlLKbI/AAAAAAAACiE/rsVnN_vV4pU/s1600-h/2012110102_53_06Windows8Activation2.png"><img alt="2012-11-01 02_53_06-Windows 8 Activation" height="367" src="http://lh4.ggpht.com/-exufLrNfjnw/UJS2O61sVFI/AAAAAAAACiM/rw4L61pT31Y/2012110102_53_06Windows8Activation_t.png?imgmax=800" style="display: inline;" title="2012-11-01 02_53_06-Windows 8 Activation" width="294" /></a> <br />
<br />
4、根据安装的Windows 8 版本选择<br />
笔者的是Windows 8 Pro，<strong>所以输入2</strong><br />
<a href="http://lh6.ggpht.com/-JnxPOIw_kGs/UJS2QHzFwyI/AAAAAAAACiU/Kcu6dg0ihxs/s1600-h/2012110102_54_38Administrator_Window.png"><img alt="2012-11-01 02_54_38-Administrator_  Windows 8 KMS激活 批处理" height="443" src="http://lh4.ggpht.com/-fgCCVcerp6U/UJS2RJOjtoI/AAAAAAAACic/jls-g3KHwx8/2012110102_54_38Administrator_Window%25255B1%25255D.png?imgmax=800" style="display: inline;" title="2012-11-01 02_54_38-Administrator_  Windows 8 KMS激活 批处理" width="677" /></a> <br />
KMS服务器地址推荐使用<strong>选项2</strong>——“kms.djxmmx.net”<br />
<br />
5、确认无误后，<strong>输入Y</strong><br />
<a href="http://lh3.ggpht.com/-nMEgbdMroUE/UJS2SWhJj0I/AAAAAAAACik/519ycWV9xAk/s1600-h/2012110102_55_10Administrator_Window%25255B1%25255D.png"><img alt="2012-11-01 02_55_10-Administrator_  Windows 8 KMS激活 批处理" height="443" src="http://lh4.ggpht.com/-EQr6WEdBXmo/UJS2TcoWQLI/AAAAAAAACis/Out5SzghWAY/2012110102_55_10Administrator_Window%25255B2%25255D.png?imgmax=800" style="display: inline;" title="2012-11-01 02_55_10-Administrator_  Windows 8 KMS激活 批处理" width="677" /></a> <br />
<br />
<br />
6、等待激活完成<br />
<a href="http://lh5.ggpht.com/-yOxvV4CEdA8/UJS2UW4fl3I/AAAAAAAACiw/qNTzbR-84go/s1600-h/2012110102_55_23Administrator_Window%25255B1%25255D.png"><img alt="2012-11-01 02_55_23-Administrator_  Windows 8 KMS激活 批处理" height="443" src="http://lh5.ggpht.com/-OrocsBIv_ac/UJS2VvBa7SI/AAAAAAAACi8/-e9YU1Bf72M/2012110102_55_23Administrator_Window.png?imgmax=800" style="display: inline;" title="2012-11-01 02_55_23-Administrator_  Windows 8 KMS激活 批处理" width="677" /></a> <br />
<br />
7、过后会有相续的提示，提示已经成功激活，点击YES即可<br />
<a href="http://lh5.ggpht.com/-nBOYJXskzX4/UJS2W7x13BI/AAAAAAAACjE/q6ztbtl1d_c/s1600-h/2012110102_55_36WindowsScriptHost2.png"><img alt="2012-11-01 02_55_36-Windows Script Host" height="155" src="http://lh4.ggpht.com/-zayQLWCgu6c/UJS2YMLDbnI/AAAAAAAACjM/hAPCZ9DjJ94/2012110102_55_36WindowsScriptHost_th.png?imgmax=800" style="display: inline;" title="2012-11-01 02_55_36-Windows Script Host" width="445" /></a> <br />
<a href="http://lh6.ggpht.com/-0A-x5vaGcTw/UJS2ZkPv4wI/AAAAAAAACjU/A525ChJTvM0/s1600-h/2012110102_55_46WindowsScriptHost2.png"><img alt="2012-11-01 02_55_46-Windows Script Host" height="155" src="http://lh3.ggpht.com/-pehoSFE9pjc/UJS2avlcHrI/AAAAAAAACjY/sqgn1v6NtxA/2012110102_55_46WindowsScriptHost_th.png?imgmax=800" style="display: inline;" title="2012-11-01 02_55_46-Windows Script Host" width="473" /></a> <br />
<a href="http://lh4.ggpht.com/-SFGBUdwqswo/UJS2bgaVGlI/AAAAAAAACjk/C8ZjxoQkKW8/s1600-h/2012110102_56_03WindowsScriptHost2.png"><img alt="2012-11-01 02_56_03-Windows Script Host" height="185" src="http://lh5.ggpht.com/-gnkEHJxaxTE/UJS2c5_9O4I/AAAAAAAACjo/XJvVUPbB5XU/2012110102_56_03WindowsScriptHost_th.png?imgmax=800" style="display: inline;" title="2012-11-01 02_56_03-Windows Script Host" width="300" /></a> <br />
<br />
如果你的到<strong>0xC004F074</strong>错误：<br />
1、请调整要电脑的时间，选择好时区<br />
2、可能KMS服务器失效了，你得找个新的KMS服务器，然后更改！<br />
