<h3>
<strong><u>2、WMC激活</u></strong></h3>
WMC 就是Windows Media Center，现在微软提供<strong>限时</strong>免费的WMC序列号！（<strong>所以激活要赶快，否者过了时间就不能了</strong>）<br />
1、先到<a href="https://windowshardware.catalysis.com/33344/?loc=en-US">https://windowshardware.catalysis.com/33344/?loc=en-US</a> 申请一个WMC密钥，填好email 和 验证码后，点击<strong>Send My Product Key</strong><br />
<a href="http://lh3.ggpht.com/-oe12p5u0zmo/UJS2d2AHqxI/AAAAAAAACj0/b7axvjXvJYY/s1600-h/image%25255B2%25255D.png"><img alt="image" height="136" src="http://lh3.ggpht.com/-QV3Fsxg75EM/UJS2eyhP8CI/AAAAAAAACj4/z4dQGdlToVs/image_thumb.png?imgmax=800" style="display: inline;" title="image" width="496" /></a> <br />
2、然后耐心的等微软发包含密钥的邮件<br />
<a href="http://lh4.ggpht.com/-fMizXLIuu6Y/UJS2f464dSI/AAAAAAAACkE/hLio6NMHprY/s1600-h/image%25255B5%25255D.png"><img alt="image" height="560" src="http://lh4.ggpht.com/-vK1t7MKNENc/UJS2gwYc83I/AAAAAAAACkM/wF2NgZIaPf4/image_thumb%25255B1%25255D.png?imgmax=800" style="display: inline;" title="image" width="783" /></a> <br />
3、拿到WMC 的密钥后，在Windows 8 下的 Search 输入<strong>Add Features，</strong>点击<strong>Setting</strong>，点击<strong>Add Features to Windows 8</strong><br />
<a href="http://lh3.ggpht.com/-oinq3B3Mazc/UJS2iEtuWFI/AAAAAAAACkQ/dJd5J-l9i-I/s1600-h/2012-11-01%25252003_00_28-%25255B3%25255D.png"><img alt="2012-11-01 03_00_28-" height="400" src="http://lh6.ggpht.com/-uLZypdsmQhY/UJS2jSKgbWI/AAAAAAAACkc/26vKDX5AAzU/2012-11-01%25252003_00_28-_thumb%25255B1%25255D.png?imgmax=800" style="display: inline;" title="2012-11-01 03_00_28-" width="640" /></a> <br />
<br />
4、选择<strong>&nbsp; I already have a product key</strong><br />
<a href="http://lh4.ggpht.com/-OCSIVd3S4iU/UJS2lsFVJqI/AAAAAAAACkk/Z6xfZtGG5fY/s1600-h/2012-11-01%25252003_01_01-Add%252520features%252520to%252520Windows%2525208%25255B3%25255D.png"><img alt="2012-11-01 03_01_01-Add features to Windows 8" height="480" src="http://lh6.ggpht.com/-BmHEIMTYs4M/UJS2m1UO17I/AAAAAAAACko/o_uOPAaymsY/2012-11-01%25252003_01_01-Add%252520features%252520to%252520Windows%2525208_thumb%25255B1%25255D.png?imgmax=800" style="display: inline;" title="2012-11-01 03_01_01-Add features to Windows 8" width="640" /></a><br />
<br />
5、输入密钥，点击next 后，程序会自动下载安装更新，过后会自动重启，<strong>激活完成啦！</strong>